{"tid":2211696,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府自身難保 機電署層層鼠","createTime":"2020-09-21T09:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T10:32:37.000Z","uid":57677,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fadf1e3210c433f49631e8c085293d44355bc5d","tid":2211696,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLNehuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLNehuj.jpg&h=0a0c0036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200921/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200921%2F00174_001.html&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZovBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=d204c2a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20200921/00174_001.html</a><br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情尚未平息，大鼠戊肝個案卻接二連三發生，連九龍灣機電工程署總部大樓亦發現鼠蹤逾一年。消息指，該大樓每層樓都有老鼠出現，天花板亦被咬爛，惟管理層卻懶理。機電署向本報證實，九龍灣總部大樓爆鼠患，現已聘請專業公司滅鼠。有公務員工會直指，政府大樓鼠患問題並非新鮮事，惟當局一直未有嚴肅跟進，令同事每日在感染鼠疫的恐懼下工作，亦有議員狠批食環署監管外判滅鼠工作不力，令老鼠在全港橫行。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0enYJ84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0enYJ84.jpg&h=32d26db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n員工指劣況持續逾年無人理<br />\n<br />\n坑渠老鼠升格，堂而皇之走入政府大樓。有網民在Facebook專頁「公務員secrets」貼文，指機電署總部大樓每層都現鼠蹤，天花板被咬爛，批評管理層不肯正視問題，反問「係咪想佢咬爛晒啲電線，大家開唔到工先睇吓有幾多隻老鼠？」該署工程人員亦向本報透露，鼠患已存在逾年，擔心老鼠在這一年間不斷繁殖，問題已非常嚴重，批評高層及外判的物業管理人員均未有跟進。<br />\n<br />\n機電署員工陳小姐指，今年曾在辦公室見到老鼠奔走，擔心老鼠會散播細菌，同事已自行購買老鼠膠捉老鼠，至今捕獲數隻小老鼠，而同事亦有促請上司要求食環署派員滅鼠，及後未再見過老鼠出沒。惟陳小姐擔心，食環署仍未查出源頭，同事間推測總部大樓附近，年初開始有多個地盤動工，令老鼠搬家，加上公務員於疫情下在家工作，空置的辦公室成為老鼠的新居，促請當局恒常滅鼠。........................................"},{"pid":"4128f4de1b39674f93f2f74b81db782d88d5a6f9","tid":2211696,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"拿,東方日報d新聞永遠貼地<br />\n<br />\n反而蘋果日報淨係識做文宣反共新聞,冇乜新鮮感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報記者學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,做番多幾個市井新聞,令到份報紙重拾角色,當然抗爭野繼續做"},{"pid":"91d123d2cf2a6792d326524561860dcd1ed6bb4f","tid":2211696,"uid":295477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太可愛啦"},{"pid":"4862fdabf941276fdfa6f4c1e316b8d4ce130270","tid":2211696,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"金鐘政府大樓有冷氣未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2958d4a2a8fb81850eddf13e59bf4762252b14ab","tid":2211696,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91d123d2cf2a6792d326524561860dcd1ed6bb4f","tid":2211696,"uid":295477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太可愛啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"香港已經越嚟越多人養花枝鼠<br />\n<br />\n即係乾淨版老鼠"},{"pid":"703ca499bbd4a31792416c7ce15ef1a069818717","tid":2211696,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"米奇好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e81b899efbb041298f10c4154f785ad8b770575","tid":2211696,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:56:57.000Z","msg":"吱&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0c7f33a74e0352639f8ef82a25ca68ace7b885cb","tid":2211696,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e92b999673fe71f59bf9a9816c54e99d1f4f78","tid":2211696,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ple